&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Research Associate 2 &lt;/strong&gt;will be responsible for executing high-quality end-to-end workflows on the Cellanome R3200 platform in support of a variety of concierge to large-scale commercial service contracts. The RA will utilize their cell biology experience to process living cells through multi-day assays, and their molecular biology experience to convert those same cells into sequencing-ready libraries. This role reports into the Sr. Manager, Concierge Development Services. &lt;strong&gt;This is a second shift position, with core hours of 2:00pm - 10:00pm.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
